column2: select top # e.eid, e.Ethnic_background_#, c.meaning AS # from dbo.Ethnicity e cross apply openjson (Ethnic_background_#) h cross apply openjson (h.value) v join metadata.columns d on d.column_name = # join metadata.encoding c on c.encoding_id = d.encoding_id AND c.value = e.Ethnic_background_#
